title: Come home to this - Res Lease in Austin. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Short lease available - can end March, April, or May 2023.', '3 bed, 2 bath duplex in sought after Northwest Hills!', 'Updated kitchen cabinets, granite counter tops, backsplash, etc... Replaced flooring throughout (except for hard tile), Carpet only in the steps.', 'Both bathrooms have walk-in showers with frameless doors.', 'Family room features high ceiling and a large fireplace.', 'Plenty of closet space.', 'Oversized fenced private backyard.', '1 car garage with opener.', 'Across from Anderson High school and also feeds into Hill Elementary and Murchison Middle school.', 'Qualifications: Tenant must have strong rental history or mortgage payments, and credit scores over 650.', 'Monthly household income must be a minimum of 3 times the rent.', 'For roommate situation each roommate will individually need to show proof of income to be at least 2.5x the rent.', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 2644690)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Matt Clausnitzer, Our House Properties']
